<h1>Getting Back On Track</h1>

<p>Just how crazy am I? Well, tonight I wrote my own weblogging system. One of the silver linings of <a href="whaaaa">losing a server</a> is that you get to rebuild things just the way you like.</p>

<p>Anyway, this might mean I&#8217;ll start posting more. Or maybe not.</p>

<p>Either way, this site is now proudly powered by good old <code>make</code>.</p>

<p>(For those who are interested <a href="code/index.html">the code is now up</a> but it&#8217;s probably not easily usable by most.)</p>


<p><i>You should follow me on twitter <a href="http://twitter.com/aaronsw">here</a>.</i></p>
<p class="posted">June  1, 2005</p>

